      "raw_response": "```python\ndef merge_sorted(a, b):\n    \"\"\"Merge two sorted lists into one.\"\"\"\n    result = []\n    while a and b:\n        if a[0] < b[0]:\n            result.append(a.pop(0))\n        else:\n            result.append(b.pop(0))\n\n    # Append any remaining elements from either list\n    result.extend(a or b)\n    \n    return result\n```",
      "notes": null
